title: I'm From Arkansas Full Movie ｜ Slim Summerville, El Brendel, Iris Adrian, Bruce Bennett

sources.title: I'm From Arkansas Full Movie ｜ Slim Summerville, El Brendel, Iris Adrian, Bruce Bennett
sources.description: A backwards community is thrust into the limelight when Esmeralda the sow gives birth to 18 piglets. The town is inundated with people out to profit from the phenomena, including a meat packing company hoping to increase their meat production.
